 to obtain superconductors in the\nFeAs-based system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Oct 2008 19:52:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Oct 2008 02:54:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Nov 2008 14:58:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
