 with mass as small as a few times Mar's mass may produce\ndetectable signatures in debris disks for semi-major axes greater than 10 AU.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Oct 2008 14:24:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
